high_descs: Turn around, take a step forward, and turn right towards the other side of the dresser.
Pick up the CD on the dresser.
Turn left, walk towards the window, and then turn right to face the book case.
Place the CD on the bowl next to the alarm clock on the book case.
Pick the bowl with the CD up.
Turn right, walk past the bed, turn right towards the wall, the turn right towards the bedside table.
Place the bowl to the right of the lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a CD on the bedside table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the long, low black dresser.
Pick up the CD that is on the far left-hand side of the dresser.
Turn to the left and move to the tall black book shelf.
Place the CD into the glass bowl that is on the shelf.
Pick up the glass bowl with the CD in it.
Move across the room to the black night stand that is on the left hand side of the bed.
Place the bowl with the CD in it on top of the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Move a CD and glass bowl to the black nighstand on the left side of the bed.

high_descs: Turn around then turn right at the dresser
Pick up the CD from the dresser
Turn left and then turn right towards the cabinet
Place the CD in the bowl next to the clock
Pick up the bowl with the CD and turn right
Turn right and go towards the door before turning right again and passing by the end of the bed and turning right on the other side of the bed closest to the wall towards a nightstand
Place the Bowl with the CD on the nightstand just to the right of the lamp
anns.task_desc: Delivering a CD to the nightstand beside the bed in a bowl
